VDSObjectManager This class manages the cache of VDSObject and VDSClass objects.
VDSObjectManagerAdapter This class implements VDSIObjectManagerListener and provides default empty method implementations for class create, object create, object update and object delete events raised by a VDSObjectManager object when one or more classes are created, one or more objects are created, updated or deleted respectively.
